{"tid":2298800,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致移左民或準備移民嘅你","createTime":"2020-11-24T09:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T10:45:29.000Z","uid":374427,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fcff593faf433b644de36bd876ffe0619f8790e7","tid":2298800,"uid":374427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:56:14.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">無論你係咩原因而移民，都希望你唔好自責。移民唔直接等於放棄香港，有大把國際線可以打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 開始一個新聯署，毫無顧忌咁spread開去唔同群組<br />\n2. 幫手翻譯港聞去唔同語言。香港傳媒報道真相，我地翻譯比全世界知香港同中國嘅醜陋<br />\n3. 有機會嘅話參與其他國家嘅遊行示威，比佢地知香港人唔止關心自己地方而係全世界，尤其睇下幾時有關於暴政濫權嘅活動<br />\n<br />\n未必個個都做到羅冠聰黃台仰上當地議會演講或見各國領袖，但只要做齊以上三點，國際線冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家喺下面繼續比意見同討論</span>"},{"pid":"e8eea64d6fe81cecf08107e56018b8d7e630e14c","tid":2298800,"uid":134840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664fda1e5d23297494993fb4abf6535321d8da07","tid":2298800,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"197e5a35148d11cba0146df7b526f0fae1130b36","tid":2298800,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"664fda1e5d23297494993fb4abf6535321d8da07","tid":2298800,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T10:25:28.000Z","msg":"咁你係咪想香港步埃塞俄比亞後塵？"},{"pid":"b55ef1a7808b529635d58585de504d08249b5386","tid":2298800,"uid":57844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"197e5a35148d11cba0146df7b526f0fae1130b36","tid":2298800,"uid":83609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"66